<item>
            <title>[LU-3600] Streamline the userspace copytool API</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3600</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current copytool API is error prone and not fully consistent. It could be made simpler and more robust.&lt;/p&gt;

